attributes.description: This dashboard provides an overview of Threat Feed IOCs collected via Google Threat Intelligence.

params.markdown:
[Threat Intelligence](#/dashboard/ti_google_threat_intelligence-9e8de699-a623-4a1b-9f63-7d641116f531) | [Adversary Intelligence](#/dashboard/ti_google_threat_intelligence-0b0fb6b4-d250-4e31-a56a-bb872e4c7c4a) | **Threat Feed Overview**

This dashboard provides an overview of Threat Feed IOCs collected via Google Threat Intelligence, focusing on IOC distribution and threat analysis.

It tracks total IOCs. along with Unique files, URLs, domains, and IPs. IOCs are analyzed with breakdowns by feed type, severity, verdict, and score. Filters refine analysis by indicator type, severity, verdict, threat score and feed type. IOCs are analyzed by file types, countries , tags, and top-level domains to identify patterns.

Network insights highlight top autonomous system owners, autonomous system numbers, and IPv4 ranges, helping analysts detect anomalies and trends.

[**Integrations Page**](/app/integrations/detail/ti_google_threat_intelligence/overview)
